MODULE: src/services
FILES: index.js, ai-cli-service.js, alert-manager-service.js, alias-store.js, audit-log-service.js, backend-registry.js, chat-queue.js, chat-service.js, command-executor-service.js, commit-service.js, file-service.js, file-watcher-service.js, git-service.js, log-pager.js, output-pager-service.js, pipeline-control-service.js, pipeline-controller.js, plan-ingestion-service.js, realtime-hub.js, scheduled-task-service.js, screenshot-service.js, session-context-service.js, session-store.js, status-aggregator.js, system-exec-service.js, system-monitor-service.js, telegram-pusher.js
RESPONSIBILITY: Business logic layer - all domain services for CLI bridging, pipeline control, file ops, git, sessions

INTERFACES:
- AiCliService: spawn and manage AI CLI sessions, stream output
- BackendRegistry: manage AI CLI backend configurations and validation
- CommandExecutorService: execute shell commands with safety guards
- PipelineControlService: start/stop/status of dev pipelines
- PipelineController: orchestrate pipeline lifecycle
- FileService: file read, tree, search operations
- GitService: git status, log, diff, commit
- CommitService: commit workflow
- SessionStore: manage active CLI sessions
- PlanIngestionService: parse and validate feature-list.json
- ScheduledTaskService: cron-based task scheduling
- AlertManagerService: alert rules and notification
- AuditLogService: security audit trail

DEPENDENCIES:
- uses: simple-git: git operations
- uses: croner: cron scheduling
- uses: pino: logging
- imports: src/security: permission and system guards
- imports: src/pipeline-infra: pipeline state and config

